engers-start-disembarking-in-spain-all-to-be-checked-for-symptoms/articleshow/130990550.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-10T16:03:20+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130990689,imgsize-1378295.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[North Korea activates nuclear dead man's switch]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130990565.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[North Korea has amended its constitution, mandating an automatic nuclear strike if leader Kim Jong-un is assassinated or incapacitated by foreign adversaries. This revision, prompted by concerns over recent decapitation attacks in Iran, formalizes retaliatory procedures. The move underscores Pyongyang's heightened security fears amid evolving geopolitical threats.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/north-korea-activates-nuclear-dead-mans-switch/articleshow/130990565.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/north-korea-activates-nuclear-dead-mans-switch/articleshow/130990565.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-10T15:51:37+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130990560,imgsize-705441.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[US government answers major question over ICE presence at 2026 FIFA World Cup stadiums after fan concerns]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130972357.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[US Immigration and Customs Enforcement agents will reportedly not operate inside or around stadiums during the 2026 FIFA World Cup, easing concerns surrounding immigration